                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4044" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0991</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11433 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">亚朵酒店的异军突起之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Competitive Strategy of Atour Hotel Co., Ltd.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">苗莉，刘骥</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东北财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">亚朵（上海）酒店管理有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">市场定位；差异化战略；价值网络；2019百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Atour；Value network；Differentiation strategy；STP theory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，随着我国经济快速发展，酒店行业迅速崛起，尤其是经济型酒店逐渐成为我国住宿行业的主体业态。但是，酒店行业结构严重失调，经济型酒店市场规模占整个酒店行业市场规模80%，同质化明显，接近于饱和状态，而且其发展模式创新不足、产品与服务单一，无法适应客户的多元化、开放化及个性化需求，转型发展势在必行。本案例阐述了亚朵（上海）酒店管理有限公司（以下简称亚朵）通过科学的市场细分与精准的市场定位发掘新市场，进而规避竞争红海，在酒店行业异军突起的过程与经历；剖析了亚朵通过产品/服务创新吸引并留住目标顾客的具体举措；并重点围绕亚朵如何通过构建利益相关者之间的价值网络来获取和整合关键战略资源，进而实现自身高速成长、成为行业领跑者进行了深度解读。旨在引导学生通过对本案例的讨论和分析，学会系统思考“目标市场定位-竞争战略选择-战略实施”系列决策中的核心问题及内在关联；掌握基本的分析工具和分析方法；能够综合应用相关理论和工具进行战略分析与战略决策。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, with the rapid development of China&#39;s economy, the hotel industry has risen rapidly, especially the economy hotels have gradually become the main business format of China&#39;s accommodation industry. However, the structure of the hotel industry is seriously dysfunctional. The size of the budget hotel market accounts for 80% of the entire hotel industry market. The homogenization is obvious, close to saturation, and its development model is not innovative enough, and its products and services are single, unable to adapt to the diversification of personalized needs, transformation and development is imperative.This paper describes the development process and business model innovation of Atour (Shanghai) Hotel Management Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as Atour) in China&#39;s hotel industry in the form of teaching cases. It analyzes in detail what strategy and how to choose Ato. Innovation has made it possible to become a leader in the highly competitive hotel industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“市场定位-竞争战略选择-战略实施”系列决策；STP 理论、差异化战略和价值网络理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-10</td>
                            </tr>
